.TH "libnvme_clear_etdas" 9 "libnvme_clear_etdas" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_clear_etdas \- Clear the Extended Telemetry Data Area 4 Supported bit
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" libnvme_clear_etdas
.BI "(struct libnvme_transport_handle *hdl "  ","
.BI "bool *changed "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hdl" 12
Transport handle
.IP "changed" 12
boolean to indicate whether or not the host
behavior support feature had been changed
.SH "RETURN"
The nvme command status if a response was received (see
\fIenum nvme_status_field\fP) or -1 with errno set otherwise.
